@node SMan "SMan"

SMan is a Mandelbrot generator written by this author.  It is best used on a system that included AGA, or CyberGraphics and a 3rd party graphics card.  SMan (Version 3.03) can be found on Bix and AmiNet.

@endnode

@node CyberGfx "CyberGraphics"

If you have a good quality 3rd party graphics card and are not using CyberGraphics, you should get it.  This system in conjunction with AmigaDOS 3.x permits running Workbench in 8, 16 and 24 bit color depths at higher resolutions than the typical VGA resolutions.  For more information, check out the web page 'www.vgr.com'.
I have not tested it with Version 3, as I haven't been able to get a working installation of V3 of the CyberGraphics system.  Please send me email, indicating either way as to CybViewBMP's compatiblity with V3.

@endnode

